data.description: Elegant 4 bedroom home with BONUS room on 0.36 acres. The entrance foyer opens to Formal Dining with HARDWOOD FLOORING, coffered ceiling & shadow box molding. The open first floor is highlighted by dream kitchen with abundant GRANITE counters. Upstairs is the spacious bonus room and Master bedroom with TWO walk in closets. Enjoy a flat rear yard with COVERED PATIO.
